C++ comments
 comments can be used to explain c++ code, and to make it more readable. 
 comments are very importente to be in your code because that hepe you and athore programes to understund 
 the code and the algorithwme that you use to solve the programe,or to explaine how the function is working
 comments can be single-lined or multi-lined.

 for short comments use single-line (//).
 for long comments use multi-line(/**/).

Exemple : 

//this Line will print my name on the screen
cout << "Mohamed Ali Zeggaf\n";
